data.description: Live/work in this 3 story townhome located in walking distance to the Abacoa Town Center.  1st floor is zoned for a business, makes a nice rental income, but also makes a great den, 4th bedroom, or a home office. New tile roof just installed, 2022 a/c and new water heater. There is a bedroom located on the 2nd floor and two master suites on the 3rd level. New carpet on stairs. Abacoa is a fun place to live for all ages.  Roger Dean Stadium, skate park, nature trails, soccer fields, tennis courts,  amphitheater, restaurants, boutiques, Abacoa Golf Club are all walking distance from this home.  Abacoa Town Center hosts many events such as, concerts, food truck invasion, car shows, festivals, golf cart night and many more. Juno Beach is around 4 miles away! Perfect place to live!
